    "\"), a statement (\"I am happy today\"), or a set of instructions (\"Generate a pointby-point list of activities to do in London today, taking into account the current weather.",
    "For lunch, suggest good vegetarian restaurants around Greenwich.\").",
    "Auxiliary data such as images or text files can be provided and the text prompt can include a reference to the data (\"Describe the image\").",
    "During the processing of the prompt, some LLMs can recruit software plugins such as web search to fetch news items, or chart and image generators to create visuals.",
    "The LLM autonomously generates control commands to operate the plugins and it incorporates their output."
